Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Fruit fly battle
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043whv1
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 6 Sep 1981
California's billion-dollar fruit crops threatened by a tiny fly. The sound quality on this recording is variable/poor. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less